# basic shape
SKBEG         0.0  1.0  0.0
   LINSEG     2.0  1.0  0.0
   ATTRIBUTE  segType   $linseg
   ATTRIBUTE  _color    $red

   BEZIER     3.0  1.0  0.0
   ATTRIBUTE  segType   $bezier
   ATTRIBUTE  _color    $green

   BEZIER     3.0  2.0  0.0
   ATTRIBUTE  segType   $bezier
   ATTRIBUTE  _color    $green

   LINSEG     1.0  2.0  0.0
   ATTRIBUTE  segType   $linseg
   ATTRIBUTE  _color    $blue

   BEZIER     0.0  2.0  0.0
   ATTRIBUTE  segType   $bezier
   ATTRIBUTE  _color    $cyan

   BEZIER     0.0  1.0  0.0
   ATTRIBUTE  segType   $bezier
   ATTRIBUTE  _color    $cyan
SKEND

